{
  "stem": "6900.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we got in the shower, we couldn't stand, some of us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We sat, and we didn't want to get out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But we got out, and the nurses dried us and helped us and gave us clothes-- shoes and under clothes and dress.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they took us to a big school that had been converted, and there were all mattresses on the floor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we slept there overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The next morning, they got us up and took us to the seaport in Copenhagen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And all Red Cross were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They put us on a boat, and on the boat we had big forms to fill in-- where we were born, where were taken, everything, where we had been.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And because I was born in England, they-- but married in Holland, and the other English girl-- they put us with the Dutch group, which was natural, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Then we got to the harbor in Malmo, Sweden.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the first-- and they said, this is where you're going to say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So-- and we were all separated then, the Dutch and the French and whoever other nationality.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were separated then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the first to leave were the French.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the people from the French embassy came, and they sang And when they saw the state they were in, they were all crying.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You can imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
